@graph.name: Data from Undifferentiated Human iPSCs Generated by SizeExclusion Chromatography Coupled Mass Spectroscopy - SEC-MS
@graph.description: This dataset was generated by size exclusion chromatography-mass spectroscopy (SEC-MS) on undifferentiated KOLF2.1J human induced pluripotent stem cells (hiPSCs), in the Nevan Krogan laboratory at the University of California San Francisco, as part of the Cell Maps for Artificial Intelligence (CM4AI; CM4AI.org) Functional Genomics Grand Challenge, a component of the U.S. National Institute of Health's (NIH) Bridge2AI program. The data will be uploaded to Pride when available. This data is Copyright (c) 2025 The Regents of the University of California.
